author: sussman
msg: Make svn_client_info() use new svn_ra_stat() API for efficiency.
(svn_client_info):  simplify by using svn_ra_stat().  if an older
svnserve throws an error, then fall back to the inefficient technique.

author: sussman
msg: New svn_ra_stat() API.  Like svn_ra_check_path(), but returns a whole dirent.
(svn_ra__vtable_t): declare new API in the 1.2 RA vtable.
(svn_repos_stat): new public API, a utility to be shared by servers.
(svn_ra_dav__do_stat): new function.  does a depth-0 PROPFIND, so
there's no need to add new code in mod_dav_svn.
also 'check-path', which wasn't already described for some reason.
(ra_svn_stat): new function, sends new 'stat' command to svnserve.
